of adults by 
<bibRefCitation author="Brown, R. G. &amp; Hodkinson, I. D." box="[436,756,1397,1423]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34" refId="ref69240" refString="Brown, R. G. &amp; Hodkinson, I. D. (1988) Taxonomy and ecology of the jumping plant-lice of Panama (Homoptera: Psylloidea). E. J. Brill, Scandinavian Science Press Ltd., Leiden, New York, Kopenhagen, Koln, 304 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.1163 / 156853988 X 00241" type="book" year="1988">Brown &amp; Hodkinson (1988)</bibRefCitation>
